 ('33', '332', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, '<p>Apple Tree Partners (ATP) is a venture capital firm that invests in pharmaceuticals, biotech, medtech, and healthcare services. Founded in 1999, with a history of well-known successes, ATP closed its current capital pool of $1.5 billion in 2012 and is actively funding healthcare innovation. ATP starts companies, or invests in existing companies, with commitments as high as $250 million. The firm is headquartered in New York City, with satellite offices in Princeton, NJ, Cambridge, MA, and Los Altos, CA.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For more information, please visit:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.appletreepartners.com/\">www.appletreepartners.com</a></p>', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-07-12 04:55:12', '2016-07-15 16:25:37', 'f7075bc2-70e9-42f9-9617-2f18db93c299'),
